1. Create project folder and initialize Git:
mkdir GitDemo
cd GitDemo
git init
2. Verify Git repo is initialized:
ls -a
3. Create and edit a file in terminal(none):
welcome.txt
4. Check the file exists:
ls
5. View the content:
cat welcome.txt
6. Check Git status:
git status
7. Stage the file:
git add welcome.txt
8. Commit with multiline message:
git commit
9. Confirm file is committed:
git status
